CONJURING

Linked Attribute: ^gWillpower^N

Conjuring allows players with ^Wmagic^n ability to conjure or banish creatures.
Only ^Wmages^n can conjure elementals, while only ^Wshamans^n can conjure nature
spirits.  The higher this skill, the more powerful the elemental or spirit
can be conjured.  Any drain suffered while conjuring is reduced by Charisma.

^WSee Also: SORCERY, CONJURE^n

